### ✅ AUTH ENDPOINTS — ALL BUILT

#### POST `/auth/signup`
```json
Body:    { "name": "John", "email": "john@example.com", "password": "Test1234" }
Success: { "success": true, "message": "OTP sent to email for verification",
           "email": "john@example.com", "otpExpiresAt": 600 }
Errors:  USER_EXISTS | PASSWORD_REQUIRED | WEAK_PASSWORD
```
Password rules: min 8 chars, must contain letters AND numbers.
`otpExpiresAt` is seconds until OTP expires (600 = 10 min).

#### POST `/auth/verify-email`
```json
Body:    { "email": "john@example.com", "otp": "482910" }
Success: { "success": true, "message": "Email verified successfully, you can now login" }
Errors:  EMAIL_NOT_REGISTERED | ALREADY_VERIFIED | OTP_EXPIRED | INVALID_OTP
```

#### POST `/auth/resend-otp`
```json
Body:    { "email": "john@example.com" }
Success: { "success": true, "email": "john@example.com", "otpExpiresAt": 600 }
Errors:  EMAIL_NOT_REGISTERED | ALREADY_VERIFIED | OTP_RECENTLY_SENT (rate limited: 1/min)
```
Show countdown timer for the 1-minute cooldown in the UI.

#### POST `/auth/google`
```json
Body:    { "name": "John Doe", "email": "john@gmail.com",
           "email_verified": true, "picture": "https://..." }
Success: { "success": true, "accessToken": "...", "refreshToken": "...",
           "user": { "id": "...", "name": "...", "email": "...", "profilePicture": "..." } }
```

#### POST `/auth/login`
```json
Body:    { "email": "john@example.com", "password": "123456" }
Success: { "success": true, "accessToken": "...", "refreshToken": "...",
           "user": { "id": "...", "name": "...", "email": "..." } }
```

#### POST `/auth/refresh-token`
```json
Body:    none (browser sends HttpOnly cookie automatically)
Success: { "success": true, "accessToken": "...", "refreshToken": "..." }
```
Each refresh token can only be used ONCE. If a used token is detected, ALL sessions revoked immediately.

#### POST `/auth/logout`
```json
Header: Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>
Body:   none (cookie sent automatically)
```

#### POST `/auth/logout-all`
```json
Header: Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>
```

#### POST `/auth/change-password`
```json
Body: { "currentPassword": "...", "newPassword": "..." }
```

#### POST `/auth/forgot-password`
```json
Body:    { "email": "john@example.com" }
Success: { "success": true, "email": "...", "expiresIn": 600 }
```
Always returns success even if email not found (prevents email enumeration).

#### POST `/auth/reset-password`
```json
Body: { "token": "<token_from_email_link>", "newPassword": "NewPass1234" }
Errors: WEAK_PASSWORD | INVALID_OR_EXPIRED_TOKEN
```
All sessions are revoked after successful reset.

#### DELETE `/auth/delete-account`
```json
Header: Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>
```

